    <sys:String x:Key="LOCSsvMoveFolderExplain" xml:space="preserve">This option adds a game menu to move all screenshot files to a single folder.
If the {Name} is not included in &quot;Folder&quot;, it is automatically added.
    
Example:
A game with two screenshot folders:
- {Public}\Screenshots
- {SteamScreenshotsDir}\435790\screenshots
    
If you have the unique folder {DropboxFolder}\Screenshots\{Name}, after selecting the option in game menu, all screenshots will be moved to the unique folder according to the &quot;File Pattern&quot; and the link will be upated in plugin data.</sys:String>

